name: ToDoList Eternal
description:
Authors: Sam, Shaniza, Skylan, Tim, Will

Just a little survival FPS made for a school project. Shoot the ToDoList.cs with your magic Javascript keyboard!

WASD move

E use door/healthkit

M1 shoot

Shift sprint

P/Escape pause

It's really, really buggy and broken. Sorry.

Github: https://github.com/doublespoiler/csharp-team-week
